or its clients it invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe for its fixed income portion the firm invests in money market and other fixed income securities of short and intermed northern trust global investments limited is a privately owned investment manager the firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles banking and thrift institutions investment companies pension and profit sharing plans charitable organizations corporations state or municipal government entities and insurance companies it manages separate clientfocused equity and fixed income portfolios the firm also manages equity fixed income and balanced mutual funds for its clients it invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe for its fixed income portion the firm invests in money market and other fixed income securities of short and intermediate term employing topdown macroeconomic view along with a bottomup analysis it employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios the firm uses external research to supplement its inhouse research to make its investments it is based in london united kingdom northern trust global investments limited operates as a subsidiary of northern trust management services ltd detailed description  bank streetcanary wharflondon ¬†e ntunited kingdom phone     fax     key executives for northern trust global investments limited mr wayne george bowers chief executive officer and chief investment officer mr andrew robert clayton senior vice president and head of securities lending mr david copley head of investment operations outsourcing mr gerald j p brady cfa md of international fund administration operations and director of northern trust global funds plc ms cherry anne mccormack head of product management compensation as of fiscal year  similar private companies by industry company name region sipp plc europe i plc europe a e taylor financial services limited europe 